Boca_Raton.Fred C. Aiken House:
The Fred C. Aiken House is a historic house located at 801 Hibiscus Street in the historic neighborhood of Old Floresta in Boca Raton, Florida.


== Description and history ==
The 2-story house was designed in the Mediterranean Revival style by architect Addison Mizner and was built in 1926 by the Mizner Development Corporation.
It was added to the National Register of Historic Places on September 24, 1992.
